Text:
Some info about the video would be appriciated to post on description of the torrent.

E.G. video bitrate, audio bitrate and channels available(stereo, surround etc), video codec used, audio codec used, container used (matroska[mkv], audio video interleave[avi], MPEG-4 Part 14[mp4]..etc)

Program used to encode the video(if available), source of video

thanks for the upload but consider post the above details on your future torrents
